                            <comment id="323705" author="james beal" created="Mon, 24 Jan 2022 17:33:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is with Ubuntu 18.04 with the latest kernel source.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We are building our own packages as we need dkms support ( and additionally in this case we need HWE support 5.4 on bionic because of the the cpu ).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="323692" author="adilger" created="Mon, 24 Jan 2022 16:18:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We don&apos;t support server builds in every kernel/distribution. You should disable the server build for your clients. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It would be useful to know the exact distro and kernel version so that the server build is disabled by default in this case  &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
